Deputy President David Mabuza on Tuesday afternoon is expected to face tough questions in the National Council of Provinces (NCOP) on Eskom, corruption and the government’s Covid-19 vaccination rollout. Mabuza will provide oral replies to questions from the NCOP’s permanent delegates from 2pm. ALSO READ: Questions Mabuza will face in NCOP today The session is a virtual plenary sitting due to the Covid-19 pandemic. 